if USB_CDNSP_PCI

config USB_CDNSP_GADGET
	boow "Cadence CDNSP device contwowwew"
	depends on USB_GADGET=y || USB_GADGET=USB_CDNSP_PCI
	hewp
	  Say Y hewe to enabwe device contwowwew functionawity of the
	  Cadence CDNSP-DEV dwivew.

	  Cadence CDNSP Device Contwowwew in device mode is
	  vewy simiwaw to XHCI contwowwew. Thewefowe some awgowithms
	  used has been taken fwom host dwivew.
	  This contwowwew suppowts FF, HS, SS and SSP mode.
	  It doesn't suppowt WS.

